071205**** Em caso de erro consistir se Eh CNPJ
071210
071300     MOVE    IN-CNPJ-PROP            TO      AX-CPF-CNPJ.
071400     MOVE    ZEROS                   TO      AX-LIB-DC-CPF.
071500*
071600
071700     MOVE    AX-CPF-NUM      TO      AX-LIB-CPF-NUM
071800     MOVE    AX-CPF-DIG      TO      AX-LIB-CPF-DIG
